snippet.title: A is For Alien?! | Occult Baby Challenge Episode #1 |  Amber Enchantress
snippet.description:
Hey, lovelies and welcome to the first episode of the Occult Baby Challenge. In this challenge, we're aiming to have a child with every type of occult Sim in the game. Today, we start off strong befriending two different occults and even woohooing with one!

Music Credits:
Song: Kass' Theme, Fi's Farewell, and Zelda's Lullaby
Artist: Mikel
Label: Gamechops
Listen Here and Support the Artist:
Zelda & Chill: https://youtu.be/GdzrrWA8e7A
Zelda & Chill 2: https://youtu.be/rJlY1uKL87k
